				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/B%C3%A1t-tu%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-Yw7Ol_bL1s3AlGhfEnPyrw">Bát tuấn đồ - 八駿圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/%C4%90%E1%BB%91i-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-ph%C3%A1t-kh%C3%A1ch/poem-pzVI5C6TOWX0hyC0YZVepg">Đối trướng phát khách - 對帳發客</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/Hi%E1%BB%83u-t%E1%BA%BF-Nh%E1%BB%8B-H%C3%A0/poem-DhL43tdqwoQaQLb5wq7jgQ">Hiểu tế Nhị Hà - 曉濟珥河</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%95/author-qsdCXtvu8PM8SdkWmraV5A">Phạm Đình Hổ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%BAc-Do%C3%A3n-Minh/Kh%E1%BB%91c-T%E1%BB%AD-U%C3%BD/poem-ocrtO_2ADY3YP6HCEZWtsQ">Khốc Tử Uý - 哭子畏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%BAc-Do%C3%A3n-Minh/author-e4jgq1mPvB3W96Qec2yOQg">Chúc Doãn Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-h%E1%BB%93-ng%C3%A2m/poem-LYhlG97QUQEVUvi2jDHP1g">Ngọc hồ ngâm - 玉壺吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%BAc/poem-TPF-t_yL41NTaSrz5HIoaw">Tặng Trương Húc - 贈張旭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/author-YrFgVDhYiheqwKg7ob0-Ig">Lý Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-V%E1%BB%87-b%C3%A1t-x%E1%BB%AD-s%C4%A9/poem-9i8XaM0gzFC7E9e0G52Oug">Tặng Vệ bát xử sĩ - 贈衛八處士</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/Th%E1%BB%8B-y%E1%BA%BFn/poem-z7guycCGz02MA5Ik49qVkg">Thị yến - 侍宴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Thuy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BB%B3/author-eVhiQaGgvOZuXB8qH633Iw">Thẩm Thuyên Kỳ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%C3%A2n-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-b%E1%BA%B1ng-%C4%91o%C3%A0n/poem-9Wdl9Laji6pZu55zXmrRIQ">Vân ngoại bằng đoàn - 雲外鵬摶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-t%E1%BA%AFc-%C4%91%E1%BB%87/poem-j2VHOreuXvBMd-jucr--gA">Xuất tắc đệ - 出則弟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%E1%BB%A5c-T%C3%BA/author-Q1iBAvdMoGVZdNIyHAuy-w">Lý Dục Tú</a>)<br></div>	</div>
